# Zensical build output is committed in docs/ for GitHub Pages
uv.lock

# Docs pages generated from templates + cargo-emitted inputs by
# `make inject-docs`. Source of truth is the *.md.in template (for
# configuration.md and history.md) or target/docs/cli-reference.md
# (for cli.md), produced by `cargo run --features generate-docs`.
docs-src/reference/cli.md
docs-src/reference/configuration.md
docs-src/history.md

# Copy of the shared Catppuccin palette. Source of truth is
# crates/scrutin-web/frontend/catppuccin-palette.css. `make inject-docs`
# mirrors it here so zensical can pick it up via extra_css.
docs-src/stylesheets/catppuccin-palette.css
